snippet.title: Best VGM 1240 - Sonic the Hedgehog 2 - Metropolis Zone
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 180 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tkj57nM0OqQ
Best VGM 1992 - https://youtu.be/Xb8k4cp_mvQ

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Genesis
Sonic the Hedgehog 2 (1992)
Metropolis Zone
Masato Nakamura
